div.p:
He pronounceth all such gilty of sacrilege and in daunger of euerlastyng damnation, that withholde any tythes


from the priests, be they either bishops or kinges, or any other persons. The tenths saith he, must nedes be paid according to this saieng of the prophete Malachy: See that ye bring in all your tythe into my Barne,
                        Mala. 3. that there maye be meate in my house.
